{"tid":2179094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅晤馬克龍轉達習近平口信　強調中歐非競爭對手","createTime":"2020-08-29T01:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T01:18:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"132a958785d91e6833b7588482db5cd4d43fa6a5","tid":2179094,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"正在法國訪問的國務委員兼外長王毅，與法國總統馬克龍會面，他向馬克龍轉達國家主席習近平的口信，並轉交習近平送贈對方的書籍。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，中方願同法方認真落實兩國元首達成的重要共識，深化中法全面戰略夥伴關係，加強協調合作，早日徹底戰勝疫情，反對將疫情政治化和病毒標籤化，又強調中歐始終是合作夥伴，不是競爭對手，雙方共識遠大於分歧，中歐應共同維護多邊主義理念，維護國際關係基本準則，共同站在歷史的正確一邊。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍表示，願意深化兩國抗疫合作，同中方進一步推進全面戰略夥伴關係，共同支持多邊主義，在公共衛生、氣候變化等問題上加強溝通協作，又說期待早日再次訪華。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546633-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546633-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=00eb459e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546633-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a9844ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546633-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"910740f0a1494f2c14c88f1a4c90e99d9ac61d98","tid":2179094,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"偷野梗係唔算競爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89c87246434487b60499332c4012cecb5f28735","tid":2179094,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"習近平送贈嘅書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/cic/upload/article/image/a032ae5e-5482-447f-86fa-e0474a6a64c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2Fcic%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Fimage%2Fa03